items.name: data_in
items.value:
You <- data.frame(name = "You", x = "domWidth / 2", y = "domHeight / 2.2", nationality = "Non-Dutch", rgbColor = "#b5b5b5")
Dutch <- data.frame(name = unlist(strsplit(gsub("^,[[:blank:]]","",CLDutchOut), split=", ")), x = "", y = "", nationality = "Dutch", rgbColor = "#FF8C00")
NonDutch <- data.frame(name = unlist(strsplit(gsub("^,[[:blank:]]","", CLNonDutchOut), split=", ")), x = "", y = "", nationality = "Non-Dutch", rgbColor = "#9CD4D4")

nodes <- rbind(You, Dutch, NonDutch)
nodes$id <- c(1:nrow(nodes)-1)

links <- data.frame(source=0, target=c(1:(nrow(nodes)-1)))

c(jsonlite::toJSON(list(nodes=nodes, links=links)))
